Beastbox grunted at the fact that Incinerator was flying upwards. He
didnt have enough momentum to continue upwards. He gracefully maneuvered
out of the way of the shells, and was glad they did not detonate beside
him. He then began his decent towards the hard, coming up fast ground.

(Beastbox cannot fly :)
